{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01C5tF6VXCBy5n8S8ByMWCu6","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'll compile the complete list of files for you. Here's a comprehensive breakdown of the files in the project:\n\n1. Java Source Files:\nLocated in `/src/main/java/`\n- Over 70 Java files covering packages:\n  - `org.eclipse.cargotracker.application`\n  - `org.eclipse.cargotracker.domain`\n  - `org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure`\n  - `org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces`\n  - `org.eclipse.pathfinder`\n\n2. XML Configuration Files:\n- `/pom.xml` (Maven project configuration)\n- `/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/web.xml`\n- `/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/faces-config.xml`\n- `/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/glassfish-web.xml`\n- `/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml`\n- `/src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml`\n- `/src/main/liberty/config/server.xml`\n- `/src/main/resources/META-INF/batch-jobs/EventFilesProcessorJob.xml`\n- `/src/test/resources/test-web.xml`\n- `/src/test/resources/test-persistence.xml`\n- `/src/test/resources/arquillian.xml`\n\n3. XHTML Files:\nLocated in `/src/main/webapp/`:\n- Admin pages (admin/*.xhtml)\n- Public pages (public/*.xhtml)\n- Booking pages (booking/*.xhtml)\n- Tracking and mapping pages\n- Template pages in `WEB-INF/templates/`\n\n4. Properties and YAML Files:\n- `/src/main/resources/org/eclipse/cargotracker/messages.properties`\n- `/postgres.yml`\n- `/cargo-tracker.yml`\n\n5. Web Resources:\nLocated in `/src/main/webapp/resources/`:\n- CSS files\n- JavaScript files (jQuery, Leaflet, topbar)\n- Images (logos, icons)\n- Leaflet mapping library files\n\n6. Other Files:\n- `README.md`\n- `LICENSE.md`\n- `CONTRIBUTING.md`\n- `Dockerfile`\n- `mvnw` and `mvnw.cmd` (Maven wrapper scripts)\n- `post-boot-commands.asadmin`\n- `cargo_tracker_cover.png`\n\n7. Test Related:\n- SoapUI test configuration files:\n  - `/src/test/soapui/handling_report_sample.json`\n  - `/src/test/soapui/cargo_tracker_soap