{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01Xvd6Xcjg1vcD5Nv9zKGTkS","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have successfully migrated all 11 Java source files in the application layer from Jakarta EE to Quarkus. Here's a detailed summary of the changes made:\n\n## Migration Summary\n\n### 1. **BookingService.java**\n- Changed `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n### 2. **HandlingEventService.java**\n- Changed `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n### 3. **CargoInspectionService.java**\n- Changed `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n\n### 4. **ApplicationEvents.java**\n- No changes needed (interface with no javax imports)\n\n### 5. **DefaultBookingService.java**\nKey changes:\n- Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n- Changed `javax.ejb.Stateless` to `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Changed `javax.inject.Inject` to `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Added `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Removed EJB imports\n\n### 6. **DefaultCargoInspectionService.java**\nKey changes:\n- Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n- Changed `javax.ejb.Stateless` to `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Changed `javax.inject.Inject` to `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Added `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Removed EJB imports\n\n### 7. **DefaultHandlingEventService.java**\nKey changes:\n- Replaced `@Stateless` with `@ApplicationScoped` and `@Transactional`\n- Changed `javax.ejb.Stateless` to `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Changed `javax.inject.Inject` to `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- Added `jakarta.transaction.Transactional`\n- Removed EJB imports\n\n### 8. **ApplicationSettings.java**\n- Changed `javax.persistence.*` to `jakarta.persistence.*`\n\n### 9. **DateConverter.java**\n- No changes needed (no javax imports)\n\n### 10. **RestConfiguration.java**\nKey changes:\n- Completely refactored to remove Jersey dependency\n- Changed `javax.ws.rs.*` to `jakarta.ws.rs.*`\n- Removed custom `getProperties()` method and Jersey-specific ServerProperties\n- Now a simple JAX-RS Application class with just `@ApplicationPath` annotation\n\n### 11. **SampleDataGenerator.java**\nKey changes:\n- Replaced `@Singleton @Startup` with `@ApplicationScoped @Startup`\n- Changed `javax.ejb.Singleton` to `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- Changed `javax.ejb.Startup` to `io.quarkus.runtime.Startup`\n- Replaced `@TransactionAttribute(TransactionAttributeType.REQUIRED)` with `@Transactional`\n- Changed `@PersistenceContext` to `@Inject` for EntityManager injection\n- Changed all `javax.*` imports to `jakarta.*`:\n  - `javax.annotation.PostConstruct` → `jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct`\n  - `javax.inject.Inject` → `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n  - `javax.persistence.*` → `jakarta.persistence.*`\n- Removed EJB-specific imports\n\nAll files have been successfully migrated following Quarkus 3.x conventions, using Jakarta EE 10 namespace, CDI for dependency injection, and removing all EJB dependencies."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"71048d40-cd2f-486a-8497-0b815786fadb"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01WyDQhRp5yMZGko7MGCHZLW","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01HfBaN4xG9GGC2iXKy4hkik","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/LoggerProducer.java","content":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.infrastructure.logging;\n\nimport java.util.logging.Logger;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.inject.Produces;\nimport jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.InjectionPoint;\n\n@ApplicationScoped\npublic class LoggerProducer {\n\n    @Produces\n    public Logger produceLogger(InjectionPoint injectionPoint) {\n        String loggerName = extractLoggerName(injectionPoint);\n        return Logger.getLogger(loggerName);\n    }\n\n    private String extractLoggerName(InjectionPoint injectionPoint) {\n        if (injectionPoint.getBean() == null) {\n            return injectionPoint.getMember().getDeclaringClass().getName();\n        }\n        if (injectionPoint.getBean().getName() == null) {\n            return injectionPoint.getBean().getBeanClass().getName();\n        }\n        return injectionPoint.getBean().getName();\n    }\n}\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":582,"cache_read_input_tokens":36152,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":582,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":394},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LTomx7EQFFRmt3d5FcqNLv","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"d75b8dfb-ac44-4963-af80-2a24a8b1e79b"}
