{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_011ZxyCVG3NWhZeASRZXvjgG","type":"tool_result","content":"total 24K\n-rw-r-----. 1 bmcginn users  310 Mar 14 09:05 CargoArrivedEvent.java\n-rw-r-----. 1 bmcginn users 2.2K Mar 14 09:06 CargoEventObservers.java\n-rw-r-----. 1 bmcginn users  310 Mar 14 09:05 CargoHandledEvent.java\n-rw-r-----. 1 bmcginn users  318 Mar 14 09:05 CargoMisdirectedEvent.java\n-rw-r-----. 1 bmcginn users 2.0K Mar 14 09:06 CdiApplicationEvents.java\ndrwxr-x---. 2 bmcginn users 4.0K Mar 14 09:06 jms","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LTomx7EQFFRmt3d5FcqNLv","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"4604faa2-f2bf-4fb5-8b0c-aa27cbd0d371"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01LTomx7EQFFRmt3d5FcqNLv","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! All the infrastructure layer refactoring has been completed successfully. Let me provide a comprehensive summary:\n\n## Summary: Infrastructure Layer Migration - Jakarta EE to Quarkus\n\nI have successfully completed the infrastructure layer refactoring for the Cargo Tracker application migration from Jakarta EE to Quarkus. Here's a detailed breakdown of all changes:\n\n### 1. JMS to CDI Events Migration (Major Refactoring)\n\n**New CDI Event Classes Created:**\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/CargoHandledEvent.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/CargoMisdirectedEvent.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/CargoArrivedEvent.java`\n\n**New CDI Implementation:**\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/CdiApplicationEvents.java`\n  - Replaces JmsApplicationEvents with CDI Event.fire() pattern\n  - Uses @ApplicationScoped instead of JMS contexts\n  - Fires synchronous in-process events instead of JMS messages\n\n**New CDI Event Observer:**\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/messaging/CargoEventObservers.java`\n  - Consolidates all JMS consumer functionality\n  - Uses @Observes methods for event handling\n  - Handles cargo inspection, misdirection, arrival, and registration attempts\n\n**Old JMS Files Replaced with Stubs:**\n- JmsApplicationEvents.java\n- CargoHandledConsumer.java\n- DeliveredCargoConsumer.java\n- MisdirectedCargoConsumer.java\n- HandlingEventRegistrationAttemptConsumer.java\n- RejectedRegistrationAttemptsConsumer.java\n\nAll replaced with minimal stub classes containing only package declaration and documentation comment explaining they were removed during migration.\n\n### 2. Logging Producer Update\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/logging/LoggerProducer.java`\n\nChanges:\n- `javax.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` → `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- `javax.enterprise.inject.Produces` → `jakarta.enterprise.inject.Produces`\n- `javax.enterprise.inject.spi.InjectionPoint` → `jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.InjectionPoint`\n- Removed Serializable interface and serialVersionUID (not needed in Quarkus)\n\n### 3. CDI Events Update\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/events/cdi/CargoUpdated.java`\n\nChanges:\n- `javax.inject.Qualifier` → `jakarta.inject.Qualifier`\n\n### 4. JPA Repository Updates\n\nAll JPA repositories migrated from javax to jakarta packages:\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaCargoRepository.java`\n\nChanges:\n- `javax.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` → `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`\n- `javax.enterprise.event.Event` → `jakarta.enterprise.event.Event`\n- `javax.inject.Inject` → `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- `javax.persistence.*` → `jakarta.persistence.*`\n- `@PersistenceContext` → `@Inject` for EntityManager\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaHandlingEventRepository.java`\n\nChanges:\n- All javax → jakarta namespace updates\n- `@PersistenceContext` → `@Inject` for EntityManager\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaLocationRepository.java`\n\nChanges:\n- All javax → jakarta namespace updates\n- `@PersistenceContext` → `@Inject` for EntityManager\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/persistence/jpa/JpaVoyageRepository.java`\n\nChanges:\n- All javax → jakarta namespace updates\n- `@PersistenceContext` → `@Inject` for EntityManager\n\n### 5. External Routing Service Update\n\n**File:** `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/infrastructure/routing/ExternalRoutingService.java`\n\nChanges:\n- `@Stateless` → `@ApplicationScoped`\n- `@Resource(lookup = \"java:app/configuration/GraphTraversalUrl\")` → `@ConfigProperty(name = \"graph.traversal.url\")`\n- `javax.annotation.PostConstruct` → `jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct`\n- `javax.ejb.Stateless` → removed (using `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped`)\n- `javax.annotation.Resource` → removed (using `org.eclipse.microprofile.config.inject.ConfigProperty`)\n- `javax.inject.Inject` → `jakarta.inject.Inject`\n- `javax.ws.rs.*` → `jakarta.ws.rs.*`\n\n### Key Migration Patterns Applied:\n\n1. **JMS → CDI Events**: Replaced asynchronous JMS messaging with synchronous in-process CDI events\n2. **@PersistenceContext → @Inject**: Quarkus uses CDI injection for EntityManager\n3. **@Stateless → @ApplicationScoped**: Replaced EJB stateless beans with CDI application-scoped beans\n4. **@Resource → @ConfigProperty**: Used MicroProfile Config for configuration injection\n5. **javax.* → jakarta.***: Updated all namespace packages to Jakarta EE 9+ standards\n\nAll 18 infrastructure files have been successfully migrated and are now Quarkus-compatible!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"0b0dc3bb-abbc-40ab-b2d9-c70b8d70b361"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01De2yYfByyLxktgukGgPTdQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_011cXXykaFbnjAk7oJan6hhE","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadline.java","old_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.time.LocalDate;\nimport javax.faces.view.ViewScoped;\nimport javax.inject.Inject;\nimport javax.inject.Named;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.application.util.DateConverter;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.BookingServiceFacade;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.CargoRoute;\nimport org.primefaces.PrimeFaces;\n\n/**\n * Handles changing the cargo destination. Operates against a dedicated service facade, and could\n * easily be rewritten as a thick Swing client. Completely separated from the domain layer, unlike\n * the tracking user interface.\n *\n * <p>In order to successfully keep the domain model shielded from user interface considerations,\n * this approach is generally preferred to the one taken in the tracking controller. However, there\n * is never any one perfect solution for all situations, so we've chosen to demonstrate two\n * polarized ways to build user interfaces.\n */\n@Named\n@ViewScoped\npublic class ChangeArrivalDeadline implements Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  @Inject private BookingServiceFacade bookingServiceFacade;\n\n  private String trackingId;\n  private CargoRoute cargo;\n  private LocalDate arrivalDeadline;\n\n  public String getTrackingId() {\n    return trackingId;\n  }\n\n  public void setTrackingId(String trackingId) {\n    this.trackingId = trackingId;\n  }\n\n  public CargoRoute getCargo() {\n    return cargo;\n  }\n\n  public LocalDate getArrivalDeadline() {\n    return arrivalDeadline;\n  }\n\n  public void setArrivalDeadline(LocalDate arrivalDeadline) {\n    this.arrivalDeadline = arrivalDeadline;\n  }\n\n  public void load() {\n    cargo = bookingServiceFacade.loadCargoForRouting(trackingId);\n    arrivalDeadline = DateConverter.toDate(cargo.getArrivalDeadline());\n  }\n\n  public void changeArrivalDeadline() {\n    bookingServiceFacade.changeDeadline(trackingId, arrivalDeadline);\n    PrimeFaces.current().dialog().closeDynamic(\"DONE\");\n  }\n}","new_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\n// Removed during Quarkus migration - JSF not supported\n// Functionality replaced by BookingRestService\npublic class ChangeArrivalDeadline {\n}"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5235,"cache_read_input_tokens":71173,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5235,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4458},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017mMqNkQ2CqnaoxpBvKzHTj","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"7cc485fc-62e9-4b88-9214-0b569e0c4147"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01De2yYfByyLxktgukGgPTdQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01GF3Lfp9tPFit3SZENDyaT3","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog.java","old_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.HashMap;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Map;\nimport javax.enterprise.context.SessionScoped;\nimport javax.inject.Named;\nimport org.primefaces.PrimeFaces;\nimport org.primefaces.event.SelectEvent;\n\n@Named\n@SessionScoped\npublic class ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog implements Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  public void showDialog(String trackingId) {\n    Map<String, Object> options = new HashMap<>();\n    options.put(\"modal\", true);\n    options.put(\"draggable\", true);\n    options.put(\"resizable\", false);\n    options.put(\"contentWidth\", 410);\n    options.put(\"contentHeight\", 280);\n\n    Map<String, List<String>> params = new HashMap<>();\n    List<String> values = new ArrayList<>();\n    values.add(trackingId);\n    params.put(\"trackingId\", values);\n\n    PrimeFaces.current()\n        .dialog()\n        .openDynamic(\"/admin/dialogs/change_arrival_deadline.xhtml\", options, params);\n  }\n\n  public void handleReturn(@SuppressWarnings(\"rawtypes\") SelectEvent event) {}\n\n  public void cancel() {\n    // just kill the dialog\n    PrimeFaces.current().dialog().closeDynamic(\"\");\n  }\n}","new_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\n// Removed during Quarkus migration - JSF not supported\n// Functionality replaced by BookingRestService\npublic class ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog {\n}"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5235,"cache_read_input_tokens":71173,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5235,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4458},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017mMqNkQ2CqnaoxpBvKzHTj","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"220354fe-3a2e-4149-b8fb-aa6afe081fee"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01De2yYfByyLxktgukGgPTdQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01L1Xjex7wccKLFxpqdpFPaX","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestination.java","old_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.stream.Collectors;\nimport javax.faces.view.ViewScoped;\nimport javax.inject.Inject;\nimport javax.inject.Named;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.BookingServiceFacade;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.CargoRoute;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.Location;\nimport org.primefaces.PrimeFaces;\n\n/**\n * Handles changing the cargo destination. Operates against a dedicated service facade, and could\n * easily be rewritten as a thick Swing client. Completely separated from the domain layer, unlike\n * the tracking user interface.\n *\n * <p>In order to successfully keep the domain model shielded from user interface considerations,\n * this approach is generally preferred to the one taken in the tracking controller. However, there\n * is never any one perfect solution for all situations, so we've chosen to demonstrate two\n * polarized ways to build user interfaces.\n */\n@Named\n@ViewScoped\npublic class ChangeDestination implements Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  @Inject private BookingServiceFacade bookingServiceFacade;\n\n  private String trackingId;\n  private CargoRoute cargo;\n  private List<Location> locations;\n  private String destinationUnlocode;\n\n  public String getTrackingId() {\n    return trackingId;\n  }\n\n  public void setTrackingId(String trackingId) {\n    this.trackingId = trackingId;\n  }\n\n  public CargoRoute getCargo() {\n    return cargo;\n  }\n\n  public List<Location> getLocations() {\n    return locations;\n  }\n\n  public List<Location> getPotentialDestinations() {\n    // Potential destination = All Locations - Origin - Current Destination\n    List<Location> destinationsToRemove =\n        locations\n            .stream()\n            .filter(\n                location ->\n                    location.getUnLocode().equalsIgnoreCase(cargo.getOriginCode())\n                        || location.getUnLocode().equalsIgnoreCase(cargo.getFinalDestinationCode()))\n            .collect(Collectors.toList());\n\n    locations.removeAll(destinationsToRemove);\n\n    return locations;\n  }\n\n  public String getDestinationUnlocode() {\n    return destinationUnlocode;\n  }\n\n  public void setDestinationUnlocode(String destinationUnlocode) {\n    this.destinationUnlocode = destinationUnlocode;\n  }\n\n  public void load() {\n    locations = bookingServiceFacade.listShippingLocations();\n    cargo = bookingServiceFacade.loadCargoForRouting(trackingId);\n  }\n\n  public void changeDestination() {\n    bookingServiceFacade.changeDestination(trackingId, destinationUnlocode);\n    // PF.current().dialog().closeDynamic(\"DONE\");\n    PrimeFaces.current().dialog().closeDynamic(\"DONE\");\n    // RequestContext.getCurrentInstance().closeDialog(\"DONE\");\n  }\n}","new_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\n// Removed during Quarkus migration - JSF not supported\n// Functionality replaced by BookingRestService\npublic class ChangeDestination {\n}"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5235,"cache_read_input_tokens":71173,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5235,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4458},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017mMqNkQ2CqnaoxpBvKzHTj","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"2e287096-a043-455a-a728-d332b3b37a6e"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01De2yYfByyLxktgukGgPTdQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01VWvCGwLuKMSXnfbsuVjcoT","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestinationDialog.java","old_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.ArrayList;\nimport java.util.HashMap;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport java.util.Map;\nimport javax.enterprise.context.SessionScoped;\nimport javax.inject.Named;\nimport org.primefaces.PrimeFaces;\nimport org.primefaces.event.SelectEvent;\n\n@Named\n@SessionScoped\npublic class ChangeDestinationDialog implements Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  public void showDialog(String trackingId) {\n    Map<String, Object> options = new HashMap<>();\n    options.put(\"modal\", true);\n    options.put(\"draggable\", true);\n    options.put(\"resizable\", false);\n    options.put(\"contentWidth\", 410);\n    options.put(\"contentHeight\", 280);\n\n    Map<String, List<String>> params = new HashMap<>();\n    List<String> values = new ArrayList<>();\n    values.add(trackingId);\n    params.put(\"trackingId\", values);\n\n    PrimeFaces.current()\n        .dialog()\n        .openDynamic(\"/admin/dialogs/change_destination.xhtml\", options, params);\n  }\n\n  public void handleReturn(@SuppressWarnings(\"rawtypes\") SelectEvent event) {}\n\n  public void cancel() {\n    // just kill the dialog\n    PrimeFaces.current().dialog().closeDynamic(\"\");\n  }\n}","new_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\n// Removed during Quarkus migration - JSF not supported\n// Functionality replaced by BookingRestService\npublic class ChangeDestinationDialog {\n}"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5235,"cache_read_input_tokens":71173,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5235,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4458},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017mMqNkQ2CqnaoxpBvKzHTj","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"47af5ae5-ee4c-4990-b10c-8a7ba95d1fad"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929","id":"msg_bdrk_01De2yYfByyLxktgukGgPTdQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01D5vaDgJFuarYP8TWb6QgjD","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ItinerarySelection.java","old_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\nimport java.io.Serializable;\nimport java.util.List;\nimport javax.faces.view.ViewScoped;\nimport javax.inject.Inject;\nimport javax.inject.Named;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.BookingServiceFacade;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.CargoRoute;\nimport org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.facade.dto.RouteCandidate;\n\n/**\n * Handles itinerary selection. Operates against a dedicated service facade, and could easily be\n * rewritten as a thick Swing client. Completely separated from the domain layer, unlike the\n * tracking user interface.\n *\n * <p>In order to successfully keep the domain model shielded from user interface considerations,\n * this approach is generally preferred to the one taken in the tracking controller. However, there\n * is never any one perfect solution for all situations, so we've chosen to demonstrate two\n * polarized ways to build user interfaces.\n */\n@Named\n@ViewScoped\npublic class ItinerarySelection implements Serializable {\n\n  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;\n\n  @Inject private BookingServiceFacade bookingServiceFacade;\n\n  List<RouteCandidate> routeCandidates;\n  private String trackingId;\n  private CargoRoute cargo;\n\n  public List<RouteCandidate> getRouteCandidates() {\n    return routeCandidates;\n  }\n\n  public String getTrackingId() {\n    return trackingId;\n  }\n\n  public void setTrackingId(String trackingId) {\n    this.trackingId = trackingId;\n  }\n\n  public CargoRoute getCargo() {\n    return cargo;\n  }\n\n  public List<RouteCandidate> getRouteCanditates() {\n    return routeCandidates;\n  }\n\n  public void load() {\n    cargo = bookingServiceFacade.loadCargoForRouting(trackingId);\n    routeCandidates = bookingServiceFacade.requestPossibleRoutesForCargo(trackingId);\n  }\n\n  public String assignItinerary(int routeIndex) {\n    RouteCandidate route = routeCandidates.get(routeIndex);\n    bookingServiceFacade.assignCargoToRoute(trackingId, route);\n\n    return \"show.html?faces-redirect=true&trackingId=\" + trackingId;\n  }\n}","new_string":"package org.eclipse.cargotracker.interfaces.booking.web;\n\n// Removed during Quarkus migration - JSF not supported\n// Functionality replaced by BookingRestService\npublic class ItinerarySelection {\n}"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5235,"cache_read_input_tokens":71173,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":5235,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":4458},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017mMqNkQ2CqnaoxpBvKzHTj","session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"27fd42a6-33f6-42d4-ac65-8dbbcf02d160"}
