nknownVoyageException.java - Regular exception with no javax imports\n- LocationRepository.java - Interface with no javax imports\n- SampleLocations.java - Static constants with no javax imports\n- VoyageRepository.java - Interface with no javax imports\n- SampleVoyages.java - Static constants with no javax imports\n- RoutingService.java - Interface with no javax imports\n- All files in domain/shared package - No javax imports\n\n### Key Changes Made:\n\n1. **Persistence imports:** All `javax.persistence.*` → `jakarta.persistence.*`\n2. **Validation imports:** All `javax.validation.*` → `jakarta.validation.*`\n3. **CDI imports:** All `javax.inject.*` → `jakarta.inject.*` and `javax.enterprise.*` → `jakarta.enterprise.*`\n4. **EJB annotation removed:** Removed `@ApplicationException` from `CannotCreateHandlingEventException` (EJB-specific, not needed in Quarkus)\n\nAll domain model layer files have been successfully migrated to Jakarta EE namespace for Quarkus compatibility!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"283b1393-6538-42eb-9750-26d6581bf30f"}
