{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_017mMqNkQ2CqnaoxpBvKzHTj","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a final summary of all the work completed:\n\n## Summary\n\nI have successfully completed the migration of the Jakarta EE Cargo Tracker application's interfaces layer to Quarkus. Here's a comprehensive summary of all the refactoring work:\n\n### 1. REST Endpoints (Updated)\n\n**Files Refactored:**\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/rest/HandlingReportService.java`\n  - Changed `@Stateless` to `@ApplicationScoped` and added `@Transactional`\n  - Replaced all `javax.*` imports with `jakarta.*`\n\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/rest/HandlingReport.java`\n  - Updated `javax.validation.*` to `jakarta.validation.*`\n  - Updated `javax.xml.bind.*` to `jakarta.xml.bind.*`\n\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/HandlingEventRegistrationAttempt.java`\n  - No javax imports (already clean)\n\n### 2. Pathfinder API (Updated)\n\n**Files Refactored:**\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/api/GraphTraversalService.java`\n  - Changed `@Stateless` to `@ApplicationScoped`\n  - Replaced all `javax.*` imports with `jakarta.*`\n\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/pathfinder/a