kus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/CargoDetails.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadline.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeArrivalDeadlineDialog.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestination.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ChangeDestinationDialog.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/booking/web/ItinerarySelection.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/FacesConfiguration.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/handling/mobile/EventLogger.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__cargotracker__jakarta__quarkus/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/eclipse/cargotracker/interfaces/tracking/web/Track.java`\n\nAll JSF files have been replaced with minimal stub classes noting that the functionality has been replaced by REST services.\n