{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WgAeDkvMbzoUaMZe84wNBy","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE -> Quarkus 3.17.7\n\n### Results\n- **11/11 smoke tests pass**\n- Application starts in ~3.5 seconds on JVM\n- Docker image builds and runs successfully\n\n### Key Changes Made in This Session\n1. **Fixed Maven artifact name**: `quarkus-resteasy-reactive-jackson` -> `quarkus-rest-jackson` (renamed in Quarkus 3.9+)\n2. **Fixed startup transaction error**: `@PostConstruct` + `@Transactional` doesn't work in Quarkus because `@PostConstruct` runs before CDI interceptors are applied. Changed to `@Observes StartupEvent` which properly supports `@Transactional` interception.\n\n### Errors Encountered & Resolved\n| Error | Root Cause | Fix |\n|-------|-----------|-----|\n| `dependency.version missing for quarkus-resteasy-reactive-jackson` | Artifact renamed in Quarkus 3.9+ | Changed to `quarkus-rest-jackson` |\n| `TransactionRequiredException: no transaction is in progress` | `@PostConstruct` bypasses CDI interceptors | Used `@Observes StartupEvent` instead |\n\n### Files Modified\n- `pom.xml` - Fixed dependency artifact name\n- `SampleDataGenerator.java` - Fixed startup transaction handling\n\n### Deliverables\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Full documentation of all migration changes, errors, and resolutions"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":504,"cache_read_input_tokens":68149,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":504,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":369},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8a9b0dd0-5198-4e27-99cf-ce225aa708f6","uuid":"26a2bf67-7748-4d06-9743-d2ef26cdf045"}
